race.comment: JAN'S MEMORY (1) stalked the pace from a low draw last start and fought on well to finish one length away in second (22.69) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 401m. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Can measure up this time. BOURBON BULLET (2) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (23.24) at this track in a Grade 4/5. Expected to bounce back to best. MINTER SHINE (7) was out of the placings last time when fifth at this track (23.21) but scored three back at this track (23.00). Returns to favourable track. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. In the mix. ZIPPING MARQUEZ (4) is always hard to beat when he races here at this trip.
